{"word":"Ahab","slug":"ahab","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Ahab</b> - King of Israel, son of Omri<p/><b>(1)</b> General references to<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=29'>1Ki 16:29</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=17&verse=1'>1Ki 17:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=18&verse=5'>1Ki 18:5</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=19&verse=1'>1Ki 19:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=2'>1Ki 20:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=25'>1Ki 21:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=3'>1Ki 22:3</a><p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=37'>1Ki 20:37</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=1'>2Ki 10:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=10&verse=10'>2Ki 10:10</a><p/><b>(2)</b> Facts Concerning<p/>Established Idolatry<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=16&verse=30'>1Ki 16:30-33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=26'>1Ki 21:26</a><p/>Was weak-minded<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=4'>1Ki 21:4</a><p/>The tool of his wife Jezebel<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=7'>1Ki 21:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=25'>1Ki 21:25</a><p/>His doom foretold by Elijah<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=21&verse=22'>1Ki 21:22</a><p/><b>--</b>By Micaiah<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=22&verse=28'>1Ki 22:28</a><p/>--AHASUERUS..<b>SEE</b> Book of Esther<p/><a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=17&chapter=1&verse=1'>Es 1:1</a>"}]}